Post-Request Checklist 
Once your request for an RCE account has been aproved and you recieved a notification from Nisha/Ben, complete the following: 
1. Read the RCE User Guide (found here on GitHub) 
2. Add yourself to the Project Directory
  -your name
  -your role (student, post-doc, etc.)
  -your affiliation (what project will you be working on)
  -the data set you are requesting/will be working on
3. Schedule a meeting with Ben regarding how to navigate the RCE
